data.description: Welcome home to the Gated Community of Colorado Bay Club in Laughlin! This 2 Bedroom 2 Bath has a cozy wood burning fireplace in the living room and his and hers closet in the master bedroom. THIS... Condo is just waiting for you to come spend some quality time for yourself! The gated community features all the things you will need on those hot summer days. And it is tucked away in the hills so you can enjoy your privacy at night. Not age restricted, 2nd story with NEW FLOORING. Ask the HOA about the available BOAT and RV Parking. Community has a heated pool. More pictures to come soon...
